title: The Story of Modern Art (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
The Story of Modern Art
The Viking Press | 1945 | ISBN: N/A | English | 664 pages | PDF | 118 MB

This book is a narrative account of the development of the art that is in the mid-twentieth century called modem. It is, so far as possible, factual and tangible. Special pains have been taken to illustrate the text amply with pictures by the many painters who have contributed to the development of modernism
